<FILEID>AP-NR-11-20-89 1135EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>u f PM-WallStreet11am     11-20 0286</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Wall Street 11am,0302</SECOND>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Aerospace stocks showed some of the biggest
losses as the stock market declined broadly today.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 16.57 to
2,636.09 by 11 a.m. on Wall Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by nearly 2 to 1 in nationwide
