<HEAD>Grain, Soybean Lower; Dry Weather Sends Wheat Prices Higher</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Grain and soybean futures opened mostly lower
today on the Chicago Board of Trade.
   Wheat was higher on concerns about dryness in the winter wheat
