   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
slumped 1.25 to 188.03.
   Standard &amp; Poor's industrial index fell 2.65 to 387.27, and
S&amp;P's 500-stock composite index was down 2.26 at 339.35.
   The NASDAQ composite index for the over-the-counter market
